      • ProxySnifferVarSourceWebSocketPlugin

        public ProxySnifferVarSourceWebSocketPlugin(int pluginNr,
                                    int initScope)
        Create a new initialized instance which is not bound to any item of the recoded session. Generate also an unique ID for this instance.
        Parameters:
        pluginNr - the plugin number helps in Code generation, its existing ProxySnifferVarSourceWebSocketPlugin + 1
        initScope - the initialization scope of the plugin. Note that this value cannot be modified belatedly.
        See Also:
        INIT_SCOPE_GLOBAL_START, INIT_SCOPE_USER_START, INIT_SCOPE_LOOP_START
